data.description: Ever dreamed of living on the water?! Well, here's an amazing opportunity! Enjoy everyday living on the Edisto River, the perfect vacation spot or a source of secondary income! With 375' of Riverfront right outside your backdoor, there are endless activities including fishing, floating, kayaking, tubing, boating and the list goes on! With your own boat ramp, small dock and large completely screened outdoor entertainment area below the home, you will never want to leave! Recently added custom built bar, tons of lighting, half bath and large workshop/storage room compliment the area. There's an attached three car carport below the home, but if you  need additional parking for a camper, RV, boat, four wheeler or room for horses, chickens, etc., there's plenty of room on your expansive 2.33acres!   This well maintained three bedroom, two and a half bath boasts high ceilings that accent the open floor plan, large kitchen with island, pantry, laundry room and large family room with stone accented wood burning fireplace! The current owners recently replaced all of the flooring with upgraded LVP (luxury vinyl plank) and ceramic tile, installed a whole home water filtration system, gas range, tankless water heater, dishwasher, new kitchen and bathroom faucets and lighting, ceiling fans, gate at entrance to the property and partial wood privacy fence.   Come see this Riverfront Oasis today!
